title: "Site Plan Checkout Eperience - August 6, 2024"
published_date: "2024-06-08"
categories: [No action Required]

Pantheon has updated the user flow for the site plan upgrade and downgrade experience. The site plan checkout built to improve on the following:
- Align with the Pantheon Design System
- Adhere to our accessibility standards 
- Improve usability and visability of the site plan checkout 

Please access our Pantheon Docs for instructructions on how to view the new site plan checkout experience (https://docs.pantheon.io/guides/launch/plans/).
